            "id": "https://kimgabe.github.io/2025/07/18/Pandas-%EA%B8%B0%EC%B4%88-01/",
            "url": "https://kimgabe.github.io/2025/07/18/Pandas-%EA%B8%B0%EC%B4%88-01/",
            "title": "[Pandas] 01. Series 데이터 생성하기(with index, value)",
            "date_published": "2025-07-17T15:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"summary\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#summary\">#</a> 🚦Summary</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pandas 기초 톺아보기 시리즈 첫번째 포스팅입니다.</li>\n<li>Pandas의 기본 객체중 하나인 Series를 다루는 방법을 소개합니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> numpy <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> np</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> pandas <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> pd</pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr />\n<h1 id=\"series\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#series\">#</a> Series</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>pandas의 기본 객체 중 하나</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>numpy의 ndarray를 기반으로 인덱싱을 기능을 추가하여 1차원 배열을 나타냄</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>index를 지정하지 않을 시, 기본적으로 ndarray와 같이 0-based 인덱스 생성, 지정할 경우 명시적으로 지정된 index를 사용</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>같은 타입의 0개 이상의 데이터를 가질 수 있음</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>실제 분석에서 생성하는 경우는 거의 없다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>DataFrame에서 파생되는 경우는 많음</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"data로만-생성하기\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#data로만-생성하기\">#</a> data로만 생성하기</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>index는 기본적으로 0부터 자동적으로 생성</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># int로 생성</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>s1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> pd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Series<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>s1</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 좌측이 index, 우측이 value</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>0    1<br />\n1    2<br />\n2    3<br />\ndtype: int64</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># str형태로 생성</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>s2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> pd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Series<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'b'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'c'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>s2</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>0    a<br />\n1    b<br />\n2    c<br />\ndtype: object</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 0 ~ 199 값으로 ndarray로 생성</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>s3 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> pd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Series<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>arange<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>s3</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>0        0<br />\n1        1<br />\n2        2<br />\n3        3<br />\n4        4<br />\n...<br />\n195    195<br />\n196    196<br />\n197    197<br />\n198    198<br />\n199    199<br />\nLength: 200, dtype: int32</p>\n<h2 id=\"data-index함께-명시하기\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#data-index함께-명시하기\">#</a> data, index함께 명시하기</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 앞부분이 value, 뒷부분이 index</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>s4 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> pd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Series<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">300</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>s4</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>100    1<br />\n200    2<br />\n300    3<br />\ndtype: int64</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>s5 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> pd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Series<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'m'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'k'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>s5</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>a    1<br />\nm    2<br />\nk    3<br />\ndtype: int64</p>\n<h2 id=\"data-index-data-type-함께-명시하기\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#data-index-data-type-함께-명시하기\">#</a> data, index, data type 함께 명시하기</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># data, index, data type 순서로 입력</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>s6 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> pd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Series<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>arange<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>arange<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">105</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> dtype<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>int16<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>s6</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>100    0<br />\n101    1<br />\n102    2<br />\n103    3<br />\n104    4<br />\ndtype: int16</p>\n<h1 id=\"인덱스-활용하기\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#인덱스-활용하기\">#</a> 인덱스 활용하기</h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># Series 에서 index값만 출력 가능</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>s6<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>index</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Int64Index([100, 101, 102, 103, 104], dtype='int64')</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># Series에서 values만 출력 가능</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>s6<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>values</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>array([0, 1, 2, 3, 4], dtype=int16)</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-인덱스를-통한-데이터-접근\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#1-인덱스를-통한-데이터-접근\">#</a> 1. 인덱스를 통한 데이터 접근</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># s6이라는 Series 에서 104라는 인덱스의 value출력</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>s6<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">104</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>4</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 105라는 인덱스의 value출력</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># 105라는 인덱스는 존재하지 않기 때문에 에러가 난다.</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>s6<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">105</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"2-인덱스를-통한-데이터-업데이트\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#2-인덱스를-통한-데이터-업데이트\">#</a> 2. 인덱스를 통한 데이터 업데이트</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>s6<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">104</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">70</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>s6</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>100     0<br />\n101     1<br />\n102     2<br />\n103     3<br />\n104    70<br />\ndtype: int16</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>s6<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">105</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">90</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>s6<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">80</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>s6</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>100     0<br />\n101     1<br />\n102     2<br />\n103     3<br />\n104    70<br />\n105    90<br />\n200    80<br />\ndtype: int64</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-인덱스-재사용하기\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#3-인덱스-재사용하기\">#</a> 3. 인덱스 재사용하기</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\"># s6의 인덱스를 s7에 활용</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>s7 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> pd<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Series<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>arange<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> s6<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>index<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>s7</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>100    0<br />\n101    1<br />\n102    2<br />\n103    3<br />\n104    4<br />\n105    5<br />\n200    6<br />\ndtype: int32</p>\n",
            "tags": [
